course_title: Stress and Strategies to Promote Well Being

101.comments: IF course is FULL please contact School of Nursing Student Support Office (student.services@nursing.ubc.ca)NURS 180 Stress and Strategies to Promote Wellbeing. Introduction to foundational knowledge related to stress, stressors, resilience, social support, and strategies to foster physical, mental, emotional, and spiritual health. Open to all students interested in learning about managing and navigating the stressors of student life.
